/eclipse73it\" class=\"reviewer-name\">eclipse73it</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Plugin per i form ne ho provati parecchi, fortunatamente non li ho acquistati, perché CF7 rimane eccezionale per pochi buoni motivi: è semplice da utilizzare; è gratuito, cosa che altri plugin non sono e pur essendo gratuito ha tutte le funzionalità che uno vuole; è leggero e non va ad influire sulla funzionalità del sito o di altri plugin e grazie agli shortcodes può essere integrato anche con plugin di page builder senza problemi.\nOvviamente bisogna masticare un po\' di codice HTML e CSS per adattarlo alle proprie necessità, ma si può anche installare il plugin CF7 Smart Grid Design Extension per le lacune.\nOttima l\'integrazione col nuovo ReChaptcha v3, non serve più selezionare l\'odiosa casella di verifica perché fa tutto in totale autonomia.\nUnica pecca è l\'aggiornamento, ma non per questo gli do meno di 5 stelle!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Contact form</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cezardobre\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/138a1e5ab435c47e88fae5a4f9864dcb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/138a1e5ab435c47e88fae5a4f9864dcb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cezardobre\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Cezar Dobre <small>(cezardobre)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I used it and it\'s very good.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solid and easy to use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mnelson4\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3f104c7c0fbf002b1ea896dc81608ec?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c3f104c7c0fbf002b1ea896dc81608ec?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mnelson4\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Michael Nelson <small>(mnelson4)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Just a solid contact form that I end up installing everywhere.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Dead</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsideserf\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b01499b10a94a46d981f84836a261ea?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b01499b10a94a46d981f84836a261ea?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsideserf\" class=\"reviewer-name\">scsatx <small>(dsideserf)</small></a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The post function runs before the field validation (should be the other way around), and recaptcha is broken. Looks like the creator is MIA. Shame.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Force reCaptcha v3 ... it&#039;s a shame !!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ciwib\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1d43fc3ff6891baa39ed5ef872227a9e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1d43fc3ff6891baa39ed5ef872227a9e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ciwib\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ciwib</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 16, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was using CF7 since several years ... and all was OK.\nBut it\'s absolutely a shame to force the use of reCaptcha v3 with the 5.1 update of the plugin.\nThe reCaptcha v3 is actually a shit.\nYou are completely crazy to break compatibility in such a way.\nThe 5.1 update of the plugin SHOULD natively propose a way (configuration) to still use the reCaptcha v2.\nFortunately, another plugin (\"<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcf7-recaptcha/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Contact Form 7 - reCaptcha v2</a>\") does perfectly the job.\nThis the only reason why I go on with CF7 ... otherwise GET OUT !!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Огромное спасибо за плагин!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/polarone\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d124666db23104dc04e40e710a965f61?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d124666db23104dc04e40e710a965f61?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/polarone\" class=\"reviewer-name\">polarone</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Огромное спасибо за плагин!\nОсобенно в связке с Popup Maker + Captcha Plus BWS цены нет, можно лепить все что угодно!\n\n5.1 не отправляла письма на WordPress 4.9.7\nmail На хостинге был включен.\nПоставил версию 5.0 - отлично стало работать.\n\nВсе это частности, плагин отличный!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">reCaptcha not working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cicciodev\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a32dc8ab3c17665af81fa0cb4cfe087a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a32dc8ab3c17665af81fa0cb4cfe087a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cicciodev\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cicciodev</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A contact form without a reCaptcha is simply useless. I found a lot of post saying things like there is a javascript conflict or similar. Others says that I have to rollback to a previous version. The real solution for me was pretty simple, I\'ve switched to WP Forms.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lacks customisations</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hasinthawk\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74bd616efb0eb095eb315bd287299718?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74bd616efb0eb095eb315bd287299718?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hasinthawk\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hasinthawk</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It is enough if you\'re just looking for send a contact form email</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing. Works perfectly.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrellas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrellas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ousskham\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a13010308d81cb0d752c03dc3dfa130c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a13010308d81cb0d752c03dc3dfa130c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ousskham\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ousskham</a> el <span class=\"review-date\">April 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I donated, because it\'s perfect.\n\nKeep up the great work.\n\nThank you.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.5.1.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"screenshot-1.png\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:7:\"contact\";s:7:\"contact\";s:12:\"contact-form\";s:12:\"contact form\";s:5:\"email\";s:5:\"email\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:4:\"form\";s:4:\"form\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:134:{s:3:\"1.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.1.zip\";s:4:\"1.10\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.0.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.0.1.zip\";s:6:\"1.10.1\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.